    <div class="card p-8">
      <BcryptView client:load />
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-left space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-zinc-400">Security Standard</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
            Bcrypt is a robust hashing algorithm designed to be computationally expensive (slow) to prevent brute-force attacks. 
            It includes a built-in salt to defend against rainbow table attacks.
        </p>
    </div>
  </div>
